Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:16.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}彷彿一望無際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:23.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲傷已煙消雲散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:30.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}為了不讓這份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:38.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我會一直在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}沒有淚水的明天過後
